<db:section xml:id="DeviceType-enum">
<db:title>enum QRhiDriverInfo::DeviceType</db:title>
<db:para>Specifies the graphics device's type, when the information is available.</db:para>
<db:para>In practice this is only applicable with Vulkan and Metal. With Direct 3D 11 and 12, using an adapter with the software flag set leads to the value <db:code>CpuDevice</db:code>. Otherwise, and with OpenGL, the value is always UnknownDevice.</db:para>
